{"tid":1689512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武請入","createTime":"2019-11-02T23:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T00:11:43.000Z","uid":35892,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a594c1856470e8025bac4dd0cc69b81ee7cf8980","tid":1689512,"uid":35892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T23:53:20.000Z","msg":"希望各位要搞清楚一件事，和理非鐘意搞遊行等警察拘捕已經係必然既事實<br />\n希望大家千祈唔好係遊行既時候自發咁細gp人走去其他區行街，一定要留返係遊行隊伍入面<br />\n一黎無左你地既話個遊行會變左係好撚和平咁被人打壓，和理非最想做到既向國際賣慘會做得好成功<br />\n二黎警察部署左咁多人捉遊行d人，你地唔跟佢地部署走去其他區，佢地會唔夠人數捉你地，無辦法保護市民架<br />\n所以求下咁多勇武下次遊行集會繼續去同d和理非一齊乖乖被捕<br />\n用自己既十年保護和理非既48個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申和理非，反對甴曱使用暴力"},{"pid":"bcf37112433eadf18a868a711ec458f1408f686d","tid":1689512,"uid":35892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T23:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc301b0b94e55df261ac86aaecfda46684134d02","tid":1689512,"uid":35892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T23:56:48.000Z","msg":"留負評者講下原因好wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通你想警察捉唔到勇武？"},{"pid":"3dcdd6c8f5e3eaebf0cb9ce573953307a7beb28e","tid":1689512,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc301b0b94e55df261ac86aaecfda46684134d02","tid":1689512,"uid":35892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T23:56:48.000Z","msg":"留負評者講下原因好wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通你想警察捉唔到勇武？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T00:00:21.000Z","msg":"可能太曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65d238a331aff1b4be4fe24ceb05a5467d4f5d0","tid":1689512,"uid":35892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dcdd6c8f5e3eaebf0cb9ce573953307a7beb28e","tid":1689512,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc301b0b94e55df261ac86aaecfda46684134d02","tid":1689512,"uid":35